    <p class="p_R_Dialog" style="page-break-after: avoid;"><span class="f_R_Dialog">Matteneinstellungen (Verlegung einzeln)</span></p>

  </div>
  <!-- The following code displays Expand All/Collapse All links  below the header in topics containing toggles -->
